NAME
        bpool - print information about buffer pools.

SYNOPSIS
        bpool

DESCRIPTION
        bpool extracts information from the buffer pool table and
        formats it in a readable form. Each line of output contains
        information about a single buffer pool and shows the pool id,
        buffer size, semaphore, and number of buffers currently in
        the pool.

SEE ALSO
        getbuf(2), freebuf(2), mkpool(2)
